data.description: Discover country paradise living in this charming split-level home! With 3 living areas, a partial basement, and sitting on just under 1 acre at the end of a dead-end road, privacy and space abound! Enjoy year-round comfort in the four seasons room with a mini-split system located off of the 1.5 car garage or relax on the newer covered front porch. Indulge in the endless possibilities for fun and storage with the expansive pole barn, offering an additional 864 sq ft (24 x 36) of space. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own! Embrace the peace and serenity of country living while enjoying the convenience of nearby amenities. This home is located close to ST RT 71 for convenient travel to Cleveland or Columbus. Set up your personal tour today! my.matterport.com/show/?m=iVkbUPAAeEz
